    addPluginListener,

    defaultWindowIcon,

    getName,
    getTauriVersion,
    getVersion,

    removeDataStore,
    setDockVisibility,

} = window.__TAURI__.app

// event
const { emit, emitTo, listen, once } = window.__TAURI__.event

// dpi
const {
    LogicalPosition,
    LogicalSize,
    PhysicalPosition,
    PhysicalSize,

// image

// menu
const {
    CheckMenuItem,
    IconMenuItem,
    itemFromKind,
    Menu,
    MenuItem,
    NativeIcon,
    PredefinedMenuItem,
    Submenu,
} = window.__TAURI__.menu

// path
const {

    appCacheDir,

    executableDir,
    fontDir,
    homeDir,

    resourceDir,

    sep,
    delimiter,
    basename,
    dirname,
    extname,
    join,
    normalize,
    resolve,
    isAbsolute,
    localDataDir,
    resolveResource,
    tempDir,
} = window.__TAURI__.path

// 调用新建窗口等函数
const { WebviewWindow } = window.__TAURI__.webviewWindow
